data.message:
The Yanmar V7 and V8 wheel loaders are comfortable and reliable partners on the jobsite.
https://www.yanmarconstruction.co.uk/Products/Wheel-loaders/V7-159/
The V7 and V8 wheel loaders feature the Z-bar linkage which offers high breakout force and fast cycle times. The linkage choice was made to improve the productivity of the Yanmar wheel loader, with wheel loaders equipped with Z-bar linkage able to maintain high torque in a lower lift arm position, ideal for load application.
The hydraulic quick hitch is part of the standard equipment of the Yanmar compact wheel loaders. It is easy and very safe to operate and allows quick and smooth change of attachments.

https://www.yanmar.com/global/news/2019/06/27/56700.html

Yanmar Holdings has announced Yanmar’s entry into a definitive agreement to acquire compact equipment manufacturer ASV Holdings Inc., a designer and manufacturer of renowned compact tracked loaders and skid-steer loaders . 
Yanmar is to acquire ASV through the mechanism of a statutory merger.
Mr. Giuliano Parodi, Executive Officer of Yanmar Holdings, stated: “We believe that the Yanmar Group’s acquisition of ASV will significantly bolster Yanmar’s compact equipment offerings in the loader segment, a product range vital for success in the all-important North American market.” Mr. Parodi added, “With its highly-skilled workforce and quality CTL/SSL lineup, ASV is a great fit for both Yanmar’s focus on quality, and our growth and expansion plans in the North American and global markets as it will create a comprehensive and global provider of compact equipment with virtually no overlap in distribution networks.”

data.message:
The Yanmar V120 Wheel Loader
ARTICULATED STEERING WITH OSCILLATING REAR AXLE
https://www.yanmarconstruction.co.uk/Products/Wheel-loaders/V120-167/
When used at a densely built-up location or construction sites with limited space, the articulated steering delivers great maneuverability with its 40° steering angle.
The articulated steering also allows the bucket to approach the load in a straight line, even at the maximum steering angle. This affords the operator greater flexibility in terms of picking up pallets or setting down loads. The oscillating rear axle has a wide slewing angle of 8°, keeping all 4 wheels in contact with the ground at all times, even when working on uneven ground. The operator also sits parallel to the work attachment at all times. This means the weight of the machine is always moving in the same direction as the bucket, which in turn increases the pressure on the ground when backing up.

data.message:
The Yanmar B95W is your stable work platform.
The undercarriage combines high terrain mobility with drive power and can be configured pricisely according to a wide range of parameters.
https://www.yanmar.com/eu/dealerlocator/construction/
With a pendulum axle that has a pendulum angle of 11.5 deg., the B95W is extremely stable, even on uneven ground.
Equipped with 2-wheel steering, the B95W can optionally be equipped with 4-wheeled steering.
The float function of the dozer blade makes ground leveling and filling work easier.

data.message:
Yanmar is proud to sponsor the Dragon Gold Cup 2019!
One of the main events on the Dragon Class racing calendar, the long-running race has been held since 1937.
Yanmar's Dragon Class racing team Yanmar RACING in the YRED boat is also making a solid showing.
Having placed as high as equal first in early races, the team is now 8th, however, there is still a lot of racing still to go!
Head over to their Instagram page for updates from the team and give them your support!
https://www.instagram.com/yanmarracing/

data.message:
MAXIMUM STABILITY AND EXCEPTIONAL LIFTING STRENGTH
https://www.yanmarconstruction.eu/Products/5-to-10-t-Excavators/ViO80-2PB-177/
The ViO80-2PB is equipped with the VICTAS® system whose strength lies in the increase of the support surface and increase in tracking through the use of asymmetric crawlers. This system, patented by Yanmar, reduces track degradation, makes displacements quieter and reduces vibration. Associated with the use of a large counterweight and excellent weight distribution, it provides the same or even higher stability than conventional machines in the same weight class, as well as remarkable lifting capacities.
+ Ideal for urban jobsites
+ Dual axis position of the arm cylinder

data.message:
Powerful and efficient B95 wheeled excavator
The Yanmar B95W features an improved powerline for greater performance on the worksite.
https://www.yanmar.com/eu/dealerlocator/construction/
The B95W is driven by an EU Stave IV / EPA Tier 4 final compliant engine. Exhaust gas after-treatment reduces emissions - including nitrogen oxides (NOx), hydrocarbons (HC) and fine dust - by up to 90%.
This is achieved through an improved combustion and injection system, and a diesel oxidation catalyst (DOC). The engine does not need a particulate filter.
Automatic idling and automatic engine shutdown functions further reduce fuel consumption.

data.message:
“We are surrounded by so much water and therefore have a strong history of sailing,” says Kræn Brinck Nielsen, CEO of X-Yachts.
The company has delivered approximately 6,000 sailboats worldwide. 
https://www.mynewsdesk.com/yanmar/news/the-x-factor-370039
Its 250 employees currently hand over around 75 boats a year to customers. Many of them come to the shipyard to see where their dreams have literally taken shape in the capable hands of the skilled workforce.
Each boat is unique, but one uniting factor is that the hearts of the boats are powered by Yanmar’s series of common-rail marine diesel engines.

With the Yanmar YH700 and YH850 combine harvesters, the need to harvest manually because of poor field conditions is a thing of the past.

The wide crawler (550mm for the YH850) and high clearance ensure smooth operation, even in a muddy field, Harvesting tall or flattened crops is also not a problem with the wide range of adjustments available to the operator.
